Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:21.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century in 100 years{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Shinichi Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until just recently, I was\Na famous high school detective
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:27.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When told to cry, I laughed instead{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,known throughout the entire country!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But a mysterious organization\Nforced me to take a pill,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,turning me into Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter if I'm small!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.71,0:00:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mind is that of\Na former great detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and no matter what sort\Nof incident takes place,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:39.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century\Nin a long, long time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:45.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're leaping into a wide open world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:52.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The things I tried to\Nunderstand as a child{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:58.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}remain a mystery even as an adult{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.89,0:01:04.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm neither a hotshot\Nnor especially great{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:11.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I understand is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:16.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's neither an answer nor the truth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:23.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I have faith in is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:28.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That and nothing else {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Threatening Monthly Presents.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.46,0:01:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Shinichi Kudo, Ran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:02:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you know the\Nsuper-famous high school detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't happen to be\Nyour boyfriend, would he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Nothing of the sort!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Nothing of the sort!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you reacting the same way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just that--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's your boyfriend, isn't he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really answer that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\Nwhat could Shinichi be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since\NI last heard anything from him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The case he's working on\Nhas probably hit a hard spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But normally he solves all of his\Ncases without any problems at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that maybe he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...gotten worse at being a detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Ogawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since about 2 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,someone has been sending me toys\Nand money every month.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of creepy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because the sender's name\Nand address are always made-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toys and money, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any children?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. A 5-year old son named Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly how much money\Nhave they been sending?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1 million yen each month.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will total 25 million this month!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,25 million?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,25 million?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta loves the fact that\Nnew toys come every month,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but being sent money is too creepy\Nfor me so I haven't touched any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:04:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, I wouldn't mind\Nholding on to the money for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any ideas\Nwho it could be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it isn't\None of your patients?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Patients?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a surgeon, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it wouldn't be strange for\None of the patients you saved
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to send all this to you in appreciation\Nfor your help, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I don't remember\Nmentioning that I was a surgeon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know that, Conan-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was his index fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My fingers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have diagonal marks\Non your fingers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When performing operations,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surgeons use both index fingers\Nto sew tight sutures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over time, it causes diagonal marks\Nto appear on their index fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I performed a surgery\Njust this very morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:04:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work, my lad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This kid knows all sorts\Nof weird stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was amazing, Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was almost like--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in a gymnastics club, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only people who train on the horizontal\Nbar ever get this many blisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost like Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This came today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There doesn't seem to be anything\Nstrange besides the money...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Normally it's a much larger package\Nwith both toys and money in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time\Nit's been like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:55.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I have finished paying the 25 million yen.\N{\a6}I will be coming to get what is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your guess is as good as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't these have\Nthose line patterns on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Line patterns?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean a barcode.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any on\Nany of these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't sell these\Ntoys in stores anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it looks like some\Nhave been damaged...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, ever since\Nthe toys started coming in,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,some of them were worn out,\Nand others were completely broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, they've either\Nbeen sending used toys
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or toys that they had\Npurchased quite a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with the large sums of money!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's just an ordinary prank!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's too complicated\Nfor a simple prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And sending all that money for\Nno reason would be pointless...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then there's that letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have such excellent\Npowers of deduction, Mori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Dad didn't figure\Nany of those things out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all because of Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this letter is the only\Nclue as to who the sender is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think the sender\Ncould be trying to buy something
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from Ogawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on how you interpret it,\Nit could mean something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a painting in the hospital\Nthat my grandfather left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure they said that it\Nwas worth about 20 million yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sender must want\Nto buy that painting from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all go to the hospital\Nand have a look at the painting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may find more details!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:08:00.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Beika Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This certainly is a large hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, too, was surprised when\NI first came here 3 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was transferred here from\Na small rural hospital, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ogawa-sensei. Another one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another one this year, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning glories?\NWith the weather as cold as it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only assume that the person has\Nbeen growing them in a greenhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, they've been sending these too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the same person has\Nbeen sending these as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the flowers only come once a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On today, February 19th.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sending flowers must mean\Nthe sender is female...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The phrase associated with morning\Nglories is "a short-lived love."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you did something\Nwith another woman 2 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing of the sort!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then could it be your son's\Nbirthday or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta's birthday is in December.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's okay with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why don't we have a look at\NOgawa-sensei's medical records?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There might be a patient who has\Nsomething to do with February 19th!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May we have a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not allowed to show\Nthe records to other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we bend the rules just this once?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. I suppose\NI have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, here are all of my patients'\Nrecords for the past 3 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's nobody in here\Nwho might want that painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, would you like to see\Nthe painting for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hanging in the patients' waiting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not coming, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok. Then be a good boy\Nand behave yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The painting is quite popular\Namong many of the patients too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun!\NSomething's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's acting too strangely for\Nan ordinary grade school student!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Back then, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this dog barks\Nat all strangers then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that other time too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know this was a lighter\Nif you've never been here before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was almost like Shinichi\Nwas giving suggestions!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day Shinichi disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Conan-kun showed up,\Nin his place, almost...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could he actually be Shinichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to make sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:10:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be reading people's\Nrecords without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said earlier that the flowers are sent\Nto the hospital once a year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me think that\Nit was a former patient here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was 2 years ago when he started\Nreceiving the toys and the money,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that narrows it down\Nto patients who were here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,during Ogawa-san's first year \Nat this hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among them, there are 8 people
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who have something\Nto do with February 19th.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People whose surgeries\Nwere successful on that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or people who were released\Nor checked in on that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sending flowers most likely means\Nthe person is grateful to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they bother me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The morning glories grown with care\Nin a greenhouse, and that letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing that you could\Nfigure that much out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great work, Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Conan! Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop playing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good! She's found me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If word gets out that\NI'm actually Shinichi Kudo,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll come back to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if that happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they might go after Ran\Nand the others as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to fool her somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! A Game Man!\NAnd Yaiba's Great Adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go Yaiba! Beat up Onimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's faking!\NIt's too suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun must really be Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this sort of thing doesn't happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a science\Nfiction movie, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he really is, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Conan-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anyone you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have someone I really like!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it's that Shinichi boy\Nyou were looking for earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always been kind\Nof a tease since he was a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he's always been so full\Nof himself and a big mystery geek,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's also courageous,\Ncool, and dependable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really like Shinichi a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Game over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you wanna try, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like this sort of thing, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not! Don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't? I'll keep playing then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomoya Ogino?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:14:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ogawa-san said\Nhis son was named Yuta...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally you enter your own name\Nor the name of a character you like...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Tomoya Ogino.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where have I seen this name before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomoya Ogino, 5 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He died after Ogawa-san\Noperated on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years ago, on February 19th!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:26.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I have finished paying the 25 million yen.\N{\a6}I will be coming to get what is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The letter couldn't mean\Nwhat I think it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Bring Mr. Ogawa here right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! There's no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That tone, his mannerisms,\Nhis deductions...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all exactly like Shinichi's!\NNo question about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really find out\Nwho the sender is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it might be the parents\Nof Tomoya Ogino-kun here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomoya Ogino?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who died of appendicitis\Nthree years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People can die from appendicitis?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. If it's not detected early enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was already too late for him when\Nthey brought him in to the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy's father absolutely\Nwould not listen to me, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would he send you presents\Nif the operation wasn't successful?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're neither presents nor used goods!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the belongings of the late\NTomoya Ogino, who died 3 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, he's been sending\Nall of his son's keepsakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sending them out of hatred!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The flowers are delivered\Nto the hospital every February 19th
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because it's the anniversary\Nof his son's death!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that letter means that he's going\Nto take the life of Ogawa-san's son
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on the exact same day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your son right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wife should be on her way\Nto pick him up at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact her at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone already picked him up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They told me his father\Nhad already picked him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This can't be happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't find them soon,\NYuta-kun's a goner!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the school?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't very far from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they're still nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a present for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you really gonna take me\Nto a fun place after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. I'll take you there soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To where Tomoya is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?! Where are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been lonely\Nall by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring you a friend soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, in fact!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes! Try this on for size!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Conan-kun do that just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move and you know what'll happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ogino-san! So it was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! It was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the father of Tomoya Ogino,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who you killed 3 years ago when\Nyou messed up his operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was already too late\Nwhen they carried him--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! As if you would understand\Nthe feelings of a father
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whose son was murdered\Njust after he turned 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I had left were his remains\Nand the 25 million in insurance money!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you sent all that money...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The money, his toys, and the\Nmorning glories that he loved so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was with my hatred\Nthat I sent them all to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's your turn to feel what\Nit's like to lose your own son!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Don't hurt my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let my son go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! So you were the one\Nwho sent the toys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always take good care of them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tomoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomoya...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Daddy and the others\Nsay something bad to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the bad one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew from the very start\Nthat it wasn't his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I had to fool myself into\Nthinking it was, or else I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, little boy! I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran. Call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Please don't get\Nthe police involved!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he just tried to kill your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:20:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ogino-san. I know exactly how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I am a father\Nbefore I'm a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How lucky it was that it didn't\Nturn into a serious incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did he send the money\Nand toys for 2 whole years?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was probably waiting \Nfor Yuta-kun to turn 5 first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same age that Tomoya-kun\Nwas when he died 3 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent deduction skills\Nyou have there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm just a kid so I don't\Nreally know for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered\Nsomething I have to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on home without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:20:59.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just my imagination {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:09.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Playing with threads around my finger\Nwhile drinking lukewarm tea{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:18.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's walk lightly\Nto the bossa nova rhythm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:23.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The puzzle pieces are in my hands{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.43,0:21:29.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:39.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was in the same place last week\Nbut with different clothes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:46.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Step by step,\Nthere's no reason to be anxious{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:53.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Case by case,\NI don't care if you laugh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:22:02.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beyond the countless days,\Nshe's waiting for me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:07.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I gotta go my own way {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.27,0:22:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.39,0:22:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.52,0:22:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.70,0:22:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be hungry.\NI'll make you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.28,0:22:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.66,0:22:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear our shop teacher Kishida-sensei \Nis getting married!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That gorilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.98,0:22:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know about\Nmy high school teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, uh, you're always talking\Nabout how he's a gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.12,0:22:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't believe it at first,\Nbut I guess you really are Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.22,0:22:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.01,0:22:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just confess already! Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.65,0:23:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.06,0:23:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let it ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.36,0:23:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.15,0:23:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'll pick it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.87,0:23:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this is the Mori Detective--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.49,0:23:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.89,0:23:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.29,0:23:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.54,0:23:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! You're right--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now. Have you already\Nforgotten the sound of my voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.59,0:23:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.01,0:23:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn that Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Professor Agasa!\NI think Ran's on to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.62,0:23:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call her using my voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He shouldn't have made her\Nworry so much like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.57,0:23:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you there, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.38,0:23:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so stupid! I think\NI misunderstood things!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.62,0:23:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Shinichi. Have you started\Nusing words that old men use?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.87,0:23:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.95,0:23:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a life-saver.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.80,0:24:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many beautiful paintings!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.57,0:24:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad we came!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.22,0:24:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this! The colors are lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.09,0:24:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that expression?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.35,0:24:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's on the card that\Nhe's so shocked about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.44,0:24:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.04,0:24:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Murder of the Art Museum Owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.11,0:24:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.06,0:24:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ball Pen Observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.47,0:25:01.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.42,0:24:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't watch the next episode, you'll fall behind!
